name: Diives Style by YeiyeiArt
description:
Hi guys, after a while I bring you a new style that I think you will love. But before that, I remind you to follow my Social Networks such as: Twitter, Instagram and Pixiv and Discord!! 👈👈👈👈where I frequently upload content of my models :DDD.

The style belongs to the artist Diives who is famous for his animations and his iconic characters, for some time I wanted to create the style but I could see that there was already one in CivitAI but it was not fully updated. So I set out to update it and share it with you, I was very satisfied with the result.

⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. Currently Rapunzel, Snow White, Merida, Cinderella, Pocahontas, Fa Mulan, Elsa, Anna, Tiana and Alice in Wonderland, Ariel, Aurora, Jasmine From the Princess Series ;D” Also u have The Bonus Series with: Nani Pelekai, Lifeguard (lilo & stitch). And Tinker bell, Jane Porter (Tarzan), Kida (atlantis), Chel.

Restaurant Series: Ronald McDonald, Wendys

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. YeiYeiArt.

Or

THE NEW !! Villain Collection: Maleficent, Ursula.

⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️

ADVICE!! “If you want a commission of something in particular, whether it’s a style or a character on request, contact me via email: jeanc.romero.ib@gmail.com.”
